{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ConnectionClosed","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This is returned as soon as the close handshake is finished (we have both sent and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"received a close frame) on the server end and as soon as the server has closed the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"underlying connection if this endpoint is a client."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Thus when you receive this, it is safe to drop the underlying connection.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Receiving this error means that the WebSocket object is not usable anymore and the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"only meaningful action with it is dropping it.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"title":"WebSocketError.ConnectionClosed","modules":[{"name":"LiveViewNativeCore"}],"symbolKind":"case","roleHeading":"Case","externalID":"s:18LiveViewNativeCore14WebSocketErrorO16ConnectionClosedyA2CmF","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ConnectionClosed"}],"role":"symbol"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/liveviewnativecore\/websocketerror\/connectionclosed"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/liveview-native-core.LiveViewNativeCore\/documentation\/LiveViewNativeCore","doc:\/\/liveview-native-core.LiveViewNativeCore\/documentation\/LiveViewNativeCore\/WebSocketError"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/liveview-native-core.LiveViewNativeCore\/documentation\/LiveViewNativeCore\/WebSocketError\/ConnectionClosed","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"WebSocket connection closed normally. This informs you of the close."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It’s not an error as such and nothing wrong happened."}],"references":{"doc://liveview-native-core.LiveViewNativeCore/documentation/LiveViewNativeCore/WebSocketError/ConnectionClosed":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/liveviewnativecore\/websocketerror\/connectionclosed","role":"symbol","title":"WebSocketError.ConnectionClosed","abstract":[{"text":"WebSocket connection closed normally. This informs you of the close.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It’s not an error as such and nothing wrong happened.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/liveview-native-core.LiveViewNativeCore\/documentation\/LiveViewNativeCore\/WebSocketError\/ConnectionClosed","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ConnectionClosed"}]},"doc://liveview-native-core.LiveViewNativeCore/documentation/LiveViewNativeCore":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/liveviewnativecore","identifier":"doc:\/\/liveview-native-core.LiveViewNativeCore\/documentation\/LiveViewNativeCore","kind":"symbol","title":"LiveViewNativeCore","abstract":[],"role":"collection"},"doc://liveview-native-core.LiveViewNativeCore/documentation/LiveViewNativeCore/WebSocketError":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/liveviewnativecore\/websocketerror","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"[tokio_tungstenite::tungstenite::error::Error], but with "},{"code":"uniffi","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" support","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/liveview-native-core.LiveViewNativeCore\/documentation\/LiveViewNativeCore\/WebSocketError","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"WebSocketError"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"WebSocketError","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"WebSock